.css-1r82dot{inline-size:-webkit-fit-content;inline-size:-moz-fit-content;inline-size:fit-content;max-inline-size:100vw;} .css-1umbx1w{-webkit-box-flex-flow:column;-webkit-flex-flow:column;-ms-flex-flow:column;flex-flow:column;-webkit-box-pack:start;-ms-flex-pack:start;-webkit-justify-content:flex-start;justify-content:flex-start;-webkit-align-items:center;-webkit-box-align:center;-ms-flex-align:center;align-items:center;inline-size:100%;block-size:100%;padding-block:0 1px;padding-inline:1px;background-color:#f8f8f8;min-block-size:250px;display:none;inline-size:-webkit-fit-content;inline-size:-moz-fit-content;inline-size:fit-content;max-inline-size:100vw;}.css-1umbx1w .e1flwkbl2{position:-webkit-sticky;position:sticky;inset-block-start:0px;}@media (max-width:1069.95px){.css-1umbx1w{display:-webkit-box;display:-webkit-flex;display:-ms-flexbox;display:flex;}}.css-1umbx1w .e1flwkbl3{display:block;}.css-1umbx1w .e1flwkbl2{inline-size:auto;block-size:auto;min-inline-size:300px;min-block-size:250px;}.css-1umbx1w .e1flwkbl1{display:-webkit-box;display:-webkit-flex;display:-ms-flexbox;display:flex;-webkit-box-pack:center;-ms-flex-pack:center;-webkit-justify-content:center;justify-content:center;-webkit-align-items:center;-webkit-box-align:center;-ms-flex-align:center;align-items:center;} Advertisement

Mani Raj Lamichhane, senior director at the Nepal Tourism Board, a semi-government body, said the decline reflected disruption to flights through Gulf hubs, which were crucial to Nepal’s long-haul connections.

More than 70 per cent of Nepal’s long-haul passengers came via the Middle East, mostly through Doha in Qatar and Dubai in the United Arab Emirates, he said.

